            <h2><a href="articulate">Articulate</a></h2>
            <div class="short-description">
              Join us to use human-centered design to end language barriers and design digital solutions for accelerated English language learning. It’s hard to learn a new language--it takes time, energy and resources. San Francisco residents who struggle with English--20% of the population--have challenges finding a job and finding the time to learn English as a Second Language.  Walk away with tools, skills, and a personal mission to carry on. Three projects will be selected to receive a $1000 honorarium each when they present their idea at a future City event.<br />
              <a href="articulate" class="learn-more">Learn more</a>
